Google announced a partnership with [[NASA Ames Research Center]] to build up {{convert|1000000|sqft|m2|-3}} of offices and work on research projects involving large-scale data management, [[nanotechnology]], [[distributed computing]], and the entrepreneurial space industry.<ref name="nasaames">Mills, Elinor.
